text: Sara Fischer (born 19 September 1979) is a Swedish snowboarder. She was born in Malung. She competed at the 2002 Winter Olympics, in parallel giant slalom. == References == == External links == * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:People from Malung-Sälen Municipality Category:Swedish female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of Sweden Category:Snowboarders at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Snowboarders at the 2006 Winter Olympics
